		<title>第一次见四元数</title>
		<link>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/6359</link>
		<comments>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/6359#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 20 May 2014 20:15:42 +0000</pubDate>
