		<title>Linux bashrc备份及说明</title>
		<link>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/2489</link>
		<comments>http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/2489#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 22 Mar 2012 05:49:30 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[时见疏星]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[计算中的宇宙]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://multiverse.lamost.org/blog/?p=2489</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[以前图方便对bashrc做了些更改，为了迎接即将到来的12年版本的ubuntu（可能我会换成其他的系统，因为对unity太失望了），所以在此备份并注释。 alias部分： # lx -x for short alias ll=&#8217;ls -alF&#8217; alias la=&#8217;ls -A&#8217; alias l=&#8217;ls -CF&#8217; alias lt=&#8217;ls -t&#8217; alias llt=&#8217;ll -t&#8217; # safe rm. -i: prompt at every action; -v lists what have been done. alias rm=&#8221;rm -i -v&#8221;...<div class='yarpp-related-rss yarpp-related-none'>

Ops, nothing related to this post. Buy yourself a lottery
</div>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>以前图方便对bashrc做了些更改，为了迎接即将到来的12年版本的ubuntu（可能我会换成其他的系统，因为对unity太失望了），所以在此备份并注释。<br />
<span id="more-2489"></span></p>
<p>alias部分：</p>
<blockquote><p>
# lx -x for short<br />
alias ll=&#8217;ls -alF&#8217;<br />
alias la=&#8217;ls -A&#8217;<br />
alias l=&#8217;ls -CF&#8217;<br />
alias lt=&#8217;ls -t&#8217;<br />
alias llt=&#8217;ll -t&#8217;</p>
<p># safe rm. -i: prompt at every action; -v lists what have been done.<br />
alias rm=&#8221;rm -i -v&#8221;</p>
<p># iopen: open file with default application.<br />
alias iopen=&#8221;gnome-open&#8221;</p>
<p># gcc-> gcc -g by default. For debugging<br />
alias gcc=&#8221;gcc -g&#8221;</p>
<p># 方便访问文件夹，赋予较长的路径别名<br />
alias nutstored=&#8221;cd ~/program/nutstore&#8221;</p>
<p># update, upgrade, etc<br />
alias sagu=&#8221;sudo apt-get update&#8221;<br />
alias sagg=&#8221;sudo apt-get upgrade&#8221;<br />
alisa sagi=&#8221;sudo apt-get install&#8221;
</p></blockquote>
<p>export部分：<br />
此部分主要是为cmbeasy和gadget指定库位置。</p>
<blockquote><p>
export CMBEASYDIR=~/program/CMBEASY_Original/<br />
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/hdf5-1.6.10/lib/<br />
export PGPLOT_DIR=/usr/lib/ # This is for splash. Splash2 needs pgplot.<br />
export PGPLOT_DEV=&#8217;/xw&#8217;<br />
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$PGPLOT_DIR<br />
export PATH=$PATH:/home/marvin/program/Gadget-2.0.7/Gadget2
</p></blockquote>
<div class='yarpp-related-rss yarpp-related-none'>
<p>Ops, nothing related to this post. Buy yourself a lottery</p>
</div>
]]></content:encoded>
